768
00:58:30,920 --> 00:58:33,140
<i>Kau tak lihat apapun.</i>

769
00:58:33,200 --> 00:58:35,416
<i>Kau harus menghadapi mereka!</i>

770
00:58:35,440 --> 00:58:37,216
<i>Jangan ganggu anakku.</i>

771
00:58:37,240 --> 00:58:40,100
<i>Apa aku harus turun tangan?/ Tidak!</i>

772
00:58:44,360 --> 00:58:45,856
